Stovall- SGC 20
Dickson- SGC 10

I've seen alot worse 10s and 20s than these, but they are still pretty nice for the grade.

  SOLD. Thank you.  Payment by Money Order or Check Please. Sorry NO PAYPAL.
1st to email me gets them at [url]kindlercrew@gmail.com[/url]
Thanks,
Tim Kindler
Cards arrived today and look awesome. The Bresnahan presents much better than it's graded. They are a great addition to my collection and my first T205s.
